Welcome to my UAV Project.

You have 2 ways to analyze this project:
1st Way:
# Mission Planner Simulation ( Optional ):
1) You have to have Python and Mission Planner installed in your PC.
2) Download the CSV File called uav_navigation_dataset.csv 
3) Copy-paste the code called kalman_filtering_uav.py into your Visual Studio Code ( or whatever you are using )
4) Run the code and you will have given two files such as RAW_DATA.waypoints and KALMAN_FILTERED_DATA.waypoints on your PC. It means that you are ready to transfer those files into your Mission Planner.
5) Go to data log section in Mission Planner and choose the waypoints files
6)Start simulating the system ( If you have no idea about Mission Planner you should watch tutorials about it)

2nd Way:
# I have already made an HTML simulator for you
1) Open the GitHub file and click into KF_Simulator.html file
2) You can analyze the deviation of UAV device and see what Kalman Filter is actually doing in the UAV Navigation Systems.


Thank you for reading :)
